1 : 0);}public static int stackfull(sqstack s){return ((s.top==M-1) ? 1 : 0);}public static int push(sqstack s,char e){if((stackfull(s))!=0)return 0;s.top++;s.data[s.top]=e;return 1;}public static char pop(sqstack s){char e ;if((stackempty(s))!=0)return 0;e=s.data[s.top];s.top--;return e;}public static char gettop(sqstack s){char e ;if((stackempty(s))!=0)return 0;e=s.data[s.top];return e;}public static int mi(int x,int y){int n =1;if(y>0)n=mi(x,y-1)*x;if(y<0)n=mi(x,y+1)/x;return n;}public static int operate(int a,int b,char ch){if(ch=='+')return a+b;else if(ch=='-')return a-b;else if(ch=='/')return a/b;else if(ch=='*')return a*b;else return 0;}public static int isoperate(char ch){if(ch=='(' || ch==')')return 1;else if(ch=='+' || ch=='-')return 1;else if(ch=='*' || ch=='/')return 1;else return 0;}public static int isnum(char ch){if((ch>='0' && ch<='9') || ch=='.')return 1;else return 0;}public static char precede(char a,char b){if(a=='+' || a=='-'){if(b=='*' || b=='/')return '<';else if(b=='(')return '<';else return '>';}else if(a=='*' || a=='/'){if(b=='(')return '<';else return '>';}else if(a=='('){if(b==')')return '=';else return '<';}else if(a==')')return '>';else if(a=='#'){if(b=='#')return '=';else return '<';}else return 0;}public static int check(char c){if(c=='+' || c=='-')return 1;else if(c=='*' || c=='/')return 1;else return 0;}}
